---
import PageLayout from '@layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About Mentric — Built by Coaches, for Coaches" description="Learn the story behind Mentric, the coaching platform built by people who understand the craft. Our mission: measurable, meaningful coaching impact.">

  <!-- ─── Hero ─── -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-glow-gradient">
    <div class="section-container py-10 md:py-14 text-center">
      <p class="category-label mb-4">About</p>
      <h1 class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        Built by coaches, <span class="text-primary">for coaches</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg md:text-xl">
        We understand the challenges of running a coaching practice because
        we have lived them. Mentric exists because coaches deserve better.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Our Story ─── -->
  <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Replace with your story -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="category-label mb-3">Our story</p>
        <h2 class="mb-8">The Mentric story</h2>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Mentric was born from a simple frustration: there was no platform built
            specifically for coaching. Coaches were forced to stitch together
            spreadsheets, generic project management tools, and disconnected apps
            — losing time, losing data, and losing the ability to show the real
            impact of their work.
          </p>
          <p>
            The vision was clear from the start. Coaching should be structured,
            measurable, and beautiful. It should feel as professional and
            considered as the work coaches do every day. Not another clunky tool
            bolted onto an HR system, but something purpose-built — designed
            around how coaches actually think and work.
          </p>
          <p>
            From the very first wireframe, coaches have been at the heart of every
            decision. Every feature has been shaped by real conversations with
            real coaches — tested, refined, and rebuilt until it felt right. Not
            features for the sake of features, but tools that genuinely make a
            difference to how coaching is delivered.
          </p>
          <p>
            That is what Mentric is: a platform that respects the craft of coaching
            and gives practitioners the tools to do their best work — while making
            it effortless to evidence the impact along the way.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Our Mission ─── -->
  <section class="bg-background">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-10">
        <p class="category-label mb-3">Purpose</p>
        <h2 class="mb-6">Our mission</h2>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed">
          To give every coach the tools to deliver measurable, meaningful
          impact — and every organisation the visibility to invest in
          coaching with confidence.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="card-editorial p-8">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-light flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09ZM18.259 8.715 18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455 2.456L21.75 6l-1.036.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455 2.456ZM16.894 20.567 16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423 1.423Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Coaching-first</h4>
          <p class="text-muted">
            Built specifically for coaching, not adapted from generic project
            management or HR tools. Every feature exists because a coach needed it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-editorial p-8">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-light flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Beautifully simple</h4>
          <p class="text-muted">
            Powerful features that feel intuitive, not overwhelming. Complexity
            under the surface, clarity on top.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-editorial p-8">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-light flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 3 19.875v-6.75ZM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V8.625ZM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V4.125Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Measurably impactful</h4>
          <p class="text-muted">
            Everything traces back to outcomes you can see and evidence.
            Coaching impact should never be a matter of opinion.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── What We Believe ─── -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <p class="category-label mb-3">Principles</p>
      <h2 class="mb-10">What we believe</h2>

      <div class="space-y-12 max-w-4xl">
        <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-8 py-2">
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light italic leading-snug text-ink">
            Every coaching conversation has the potential to transform a career.
          </p>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-8 py-2">
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light italic leading-snug text-ink">
            Great coaches deserve great tools.
          </p>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-8 py-2">
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light italic leading-snug text-ink">
            The best technology stays out of the way.
          </p>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-primary-300 pl-8 py-2">
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light italic leading-snug text-ink">
            Measuring impact doesn't mean losing the human touch.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Team ─── -->
  <section class="bg-background">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20">
      <p class="category-label mb-3">People</p>
      <h2 class="mb-6">The team behind Mentric</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-lg mb-12">
        A small, dedicated team of coaches, designers, and engineers who
        believe coaching deserves better technology.
      </p>

      <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Team member placeholder cards — replace with real profiles -->
        <div class="card-editorial p-8 text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-primary-light mx-auto mb-5 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary/40" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Team profiles coming soon</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Founder &amp; CEO</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-editorial p-8 text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-primary-light mx-auto mb-5 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary/40" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Team profiles coming soon</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Role title</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-editorial p-8 text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-primary-light mx-auto mb-5 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary/40" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Team profiles coming soon</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Role title</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── CTA Banner ─── -->
  <section class="bg-plum-gradient">
    <div class="section-container py-14 md:py-20 text-center">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-200 mb-4">Get in Touch</p>
      <h2 class="text-white max-w-3xl mx-auto">Want to learn more?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg text-primary-200">
        We'd love to hear from you and show you what Mentric can do.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary-lg bg-white text-primary hover:bg-primary-50 hover:shadow-glow-lg">
          Book a Demo
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</PageLayout>
